00:22:59.295 --> 00:23:00.588 line:80%
Aren't I such a fool?

241
00:23:03.382 --> 00:23:04.884 line:80%
It's all over now.

242
00:23:06.886 --> 00:23:08.846 line:80%
Stop thinking about them.

243
00:23:09.764 --> 00:23:11.432 line:80%
Think about one thing today.

244
00:23:12.308 --> 00:23:13.601 line:80%
Kang Ji-won won.

245
00:23:24.529 --> 00:23:25.571 line:80%
I haven't...

246
00:23:27.073 --> 00:23:30.326 line:80%
had someone touch my hand
this affectionately

247
00:23:31.202 --> 00:23:32.328 line:80%
in a long time.

248
00:23:43.756 --> 00:23:45.758 line:80%
Since I came back to 2013,

249
00:23:47.885 --> 00:23:50.596 line:80%
I've felt so lonely since I was alone.

250
00:23:56.269 --> 00:23:59.147 line:80%
So I'm glad I have you.

251
00:24:01.232 --> 00:24:02.650 line:80%
Thank you.

252
00:24:09.782 --> 00:24:11.033 line:80%
To be honest,

253
00:24:13.452 --> 00:24:16.414 line:80%
my life is like a well-written novel.

254
00:24:20.084 --> 00:24:23.129 line:80%
A life without any worries or obstacles.

255
00:24:23.212 --> 00:24:24.338 line:80%
Just well-written.

256
00:24:30.219 --> 00:24:32.430 line:80%
So I'm glad I came back,

257
00:24:33.347 --> 00:24:36.058 line:80%
and I'm happy
I get to talk to you like this.

258
00:24:45.234 --> 00:24:46.944 line:80%
I should thank you.

259
00:25:00.166 --> 00:25:01.792 line:80%
You never keep it simple.

260
00:25:03.377 --> 00:25:04.212 line:80%
Is that so?

261
00:25:07.965 --> 00:25:11.010 line:80%
What did you say earlier?
What do you want to be?

262
00:25:11.719 --> 00:25:14.513 line:80%
I'll help you for helping me too.

263
00:25:15.973 --> 00:25:19.101 line:80%
I told you,
I don't want anything from you in return.

264
00:25:19.727 --> 00:25:22.021 line:80%
I'm being honest, but you're not.

265
00:25:23.272 --> 00:25:24.982 line:80%
Then I won't let you help me.

266
00:25:25.942 --> 00:25:27.568 line:80%
Let's say I said champ.

267
00:25:28.236 --> 00:25:29.779 line:80%
No, you didn't.

268
00:25:29.862 --> 00:25:31.197 line:80%
Are you lying?

269
00:25:32.615 --> 00:25:33.783 line:80%
It's true.

270
00:25:45.753 --> 00:25:46.629 line:80%
Ji-won.

271
00:25:48.297 --> 00:25:52.426 line:80%
Did you sleep well when your boyfriend was
sleeping in a sleeping bag?

272
00:25:52.510 --> 00:25:54.845 line:80%
You're so cold-hearted.

273
00:25:55.805 --> 00:25:57.598 line:80%
Did you really sleep there?

274
00:25:58.724 --> 00:26:00.017 line:80%
Where else, then?

275
00:26:00.101 --> 00:26:02.436 line:80%
My selfish girlfriend slept in the camper.

276
00:26:03.187 --> 00:26:08.234 line:80%
Weren't you even worried your boyfriend
might be too cold overnight?

277
00:26:08.901 --> 00:26:12.697 line:80%
I was, so I went to you with hand warmers,
but you weren't there.

278
00:26:16.617 --> 00:26:18.744 line:80%
I guess I was in the bathroom then.

279
00:26:18.828 --> 00:26:19.996 line:80%
Yes.

280
00:26:20.079 --> 00:26:22.206 line:80%
You could've just left them there.

281
00:26:22.290 --> 00:26:24.083 line:80%
Where's your common sense?

282
00:26:25.001 --> 00:26:25.960 line:80%
Where's Su-min?

283
00:26:29.547 --> 00:26:31.882 line:80%
How should I know where your friend is?

284
00:26:34.176 --> 00:26:35.386 line:80%
Where did she sleep?

285
00:26:37.513 --> 00:26:38.347 line:80%
I don't know.

286
00:26:39.974 --> 00:26:43.853 line:80%
Something happened between us yesterday,
and it's uncomfortable.

287
00:26:45.604 --> 00:26:46.772 line:80%
Uncomfortable?

288
00:26:48.566 --> 00:26:49.817 line:80%
Did you fight?

289
00:26:50.568 --> 00:26:54.113 line:80%
Women are always fighting
and making up. Goodness.

290
00:26:59.744 --> 00:27:00.786 line:80%
What?

291
00:27:01.620 --> 00:27:03.080 line:80%
Let's go eat breakfast.

292
00:27:19.597 --> 00:27:20.806 line:80%
Su-min.

293
00:27:22.600 --> 00:27:24.185 line:80%
This isn't your tent.

294
00:27:24.268 --> 00:27:25.978 line:80%
Where were you last night?

295
00:27:26.562 --> 00:27:30.149 line:80%
I was drunk, so I slept over there.
I just left my stuff here.

296
00:27:31.734 --> 00:27:33.486 line:80%
Did you drink a lot too?

297
00:27:34.278 --> 00:27:38.991 line:80%
I was able to sober up a bit
after a walk with Hui-yeon last night.

298
00:27:39.742 --> 00:27:40.701 line:80%
I see.

299
00:27:48.459 --> 00:27:50.544 line:80%
Let's not tell Ji-won.

300
00:27:51.921 --> 00:27:52.755 line:80%
What?

301
00:27:53.798 --> 00:27:57.301 line:80%
It's not like she'll break up with me.
She'll only get hurt.

302
00:27:59.553 --> 00:28:02.014 line:80%
You're close friends. It's unnecessary.

303
00:28:06.435 --> 00:28:08.145 line:80%
Let's just be realistic.

304
00:28:08.813 --> 00:28:12.775 line:80%
As you said,
things are too complicated between us.

305
00:28:14.985 --> 00:28:18.906 line:80%
Instead of rolling around
in a messy reality,

306
00:28:19.490 --> 00:28:21.659 line:80%
let's keep it as a beautiful memory.

307
00:28:22.326 --> 00:28:23.702 line:80%
Is it too greedy of me?

308
00:28:28.290 --> 00:28:29.500 line:80%
Let's go eat.

309
00:28:29.583 --> 00:28:30.960 line:80%
I'm so hungover.

310
00:28:31.794 --> 00:28:32.711 line:80%
Okay.

311
00:28:37.758 --> 00:28:41.053 line:80%
Why can I never get the best?

312
00:28:41.137 --> 00:28:41.971 line:80%
What?

313
00:28:43.389 --> 00:28:46.642 line:80%
The workshop sucked.

314
00:28:46.725 --> 00:28:49.770 line:80%
I wanted to sleep in a camper
or a glamping tent.

315
00:28:52.148 --> 00:28:53.899 line:80%
You'll have other chances.

316
00:28:53.983 --> 00:28:56.068 line:80%
Failure is the mother of success.

317
00:28:58.195 --> 00:29:02.074 line:80%
You're right. Nothing's impossible.

318
00:29:02.158 --> 00:29:04.076 line:80%
This is so nice!

319
00:29:10.708 --> 00:29:11.542 line:80%
Babe!

320
00:29:12.668 --> 00:29:13.502 line:80%
Here.

321
00:29:15.713 --> 00:29:17.298 line:80%
I'm so hungry.

322
00:29:17.381 --> 00:29:19.758 line:80%
Let's see the food over here first.

323
00:29:20.259 --> 00:29:22.219 line:80%
Babe, here. You like this.

324
00:29:27.600 --> 00:29:31.145 line:80%
Wow! It's been so long
since I had an orange!

325
00:29:32.771 --> 00:29:34.315 line:80%
Here's a melon!

326
00:29:36.358 --> 00:29:37.860 line:80%
Avocado! Wow!

327
00:29:40.321 --> 00:29:41.489 line:80%
Let's see.

328
00:29:41.572 --> 00:29:43.115 line:80%
Can this help digestion?

329
00:30:16.774 --> 00:30:19.026 line:80%
I don't think it went as expected.

330
00:30:19.109 --> 00:30:22.780 line:80%
I've been with Su-min for 26 years,
and 17 years with Min-hwan.

331
00:30:22.863 --> 00:30:24.990 line:80%
I'm sure something happened.

332
00:30:25.074 --> 00:30:26.033 line:80%
Then...

333
00:30:26.992 --> 00:30:32.039 line:80%
When I felt something was off, all my
ex-boyfriends broke up with me right away.

334
00:30:32.623 --> 00:30:36.126 line:80%
Min-hwan was the first to do it
behind my back.

335
00:30:37.503 --> 00:30:40.339 line:80%
I thought it was because of marriage.

336
00:30:43.509 --> 00:30:47.054 line:80%
But if Min-hwan is
more of a scumbag than I thought...

337
00:30:51.684 --> 00:30:52.685 line:80%
It means

338
00:30:53.644 --> 00:30:55.354 line:80%
it's not over yet.

339
00:31:51.410 --> 00:31:53.537 line:80%
Why are you so full of energy?

340
00:31:53.621 --> 00:31:57.041 line:80%
I hit a homerun!

341
00:31:57.750 --> 00:32:00.002 line:80%
What? With your girlfriend's friend?

342
00:32:03.172 --> 00:32:04.381 line:80%
Shut up!

343
00:32:04.465 --> 00:32:06.550 line:80%
Wow! Seriously?

344
00:32:07.760 --> 00:32:09.845 line:80%
But she's her best friend.

345
00:32:09.928 --> 00:32:11.764 line:80%
I'll tell you in one sentence.

346
00:32:13.349 --> 00:32:14.725 line:80%
Autumn was coming,

347
00:32:15.893 --> 00:32:17.770 line:80%
and the night air was sexy!

348
00:32:27.446 --> 00:32:30.074 line:80%
What the... Okay, let's try again.

349
00:32:31.533 --> 00:32:35.204 line:80%
Can you handle the consequences?
You work in the same office.

350
00:32:43.420 --> 00:32:44.838 line:80%
OUT ON BUSINESS LOG

351
00:32:44.922 --> 00:32:46.256 line:80%
PARK MIN-HWAN, JEONG SU-MIN

352
00:32:46.340 --> 00:32:48.175 line:80%
ACTIVITIES: JOMART TASTING EVENT

353
00:32:48.258 --> 00:32:49.259 line:80%
What's this?

354
00:32:51.720 --> 00:32:53.639 line:80%
You're going to Jomart.

355
00:32:53.722 --> 00:32:54.932 line:80%
It'll be tiring.

356
00:32:57.226 --> 00:32:59.019 line:80%
Why me?

357
00:32:59.520 --> 00:33:01.480 line:80%
Shouldn't you go instead?

358
00:33:01.563 --> 00:33:03.440 line:80%
Right, you guys fought.

359
00:33:05.317 --> 00:33:08.362 line:80%
Don't talk nonsense.
I have a presentation today.

360
00:33:08.445 --> 00:33:11.532 line:80%
A presentation?
The slides must be all ready, right?

361
00:33:11.615 --> 00:33:12.700 line:80%
I'll do it.

362
00:33:13.242 --> 00:33:14.702 line:80%
Is there a problem?

363
00:33:17.454 --> 00:33:19.707 line:80%
No, not at all, sir.

364
00:33:26.505 --> 00:33:28.674 line:80%
Mr. Park, shall we go?

365
00:33:29.299 --> 00:33:30.300 line:80%
Yes.

366
00:33:40.352 --> 00:33:42.271 line:80%
I'll get going, Ms. Kang.

367
00:33:53.991 --> 00:33:55.325 line:80%
Su-min's so smart.

368
00:33:56.577 --> 00:34:00.414 line:80%
She's working so hard.
I hope she becomes a full-time employee.

369
00:34:08.547 --> 00:34:10.924 line:80%
To my other half, Ji-won.

370
00:34:11.008 --> 00:34:13.469 line:80%
I'm sorry I didn't know how you felt.

371
00:34:13.552 --> 00:34:15.512 line:80%
You're everything to me,

372
00:34:15.596 --> 00:34:18.348 line:80%
and I think it made me
blind to your feelings.

373
00:34:18.432 --> 00:34:22.436 line:80%
I just blindly believed you loved me.

374
00:34:22.519 --> 00:34:25.689 line:80%
I didn't think
about whether I deserved your love.

375
00:34:25.773 --> 00:34:31.111 line:80%
So everything you said
and everything you feel towards me...

376
00:34:31.195 --> 00:34:32.696 line:80%
It's all my fault.

377
00:34:33.906 --> 00:34:39.578 line:80%
Still, can't you forgive me?

378
00:34:39.661 --> 00:34:43.832 line:80%
You're too precious to me.
I can't live without you.

379
00:34:44.416 --> 00:34:47.753 line:80%
I'm going to wait until you feel better.

380
00:34:47.836 --> 00:34:52.633 line:80%
If I knock and you ever want to reopen
your closed heart to me,

381
00:34:52.716 --> 00:34:55.344 line:80%
will you smile as if nothing happened?

382
00:34:56.553 --> 00:34:58.096 line:80%
You're my other half.

383
00:34:59.014 --> 00:35:01.433 line:80%
We can't just end things like this.

384
00:35:10.692 --> 00:35:13.070 line:80%
If I hadn't seen the end,

385
00:35:15.280 --> 00:35:17.115 line:80%
would I have been able

386
00:35:17.866 --> 00:35:20.369 line:80%
to not be swayed after reading this?

387
00:35:33.131 --> 00:35:34.550 line:80%
She's a good writer.

388
00:35:39.721 --> 00:35:42.432 line:80%
Maybe she really means it.

389
00:35:59.616 --> 00:36:01.785 line:80%
-You're doing well. Hurry up.
-Yes, Chef.

390
00:36:31.064 --> 00:36:32.858 line:80%
I don't want to see you face.

391
00:36:33.775 --> 00:36:34.776 line:80%
I'm jealous.

392
00:36:41.116 --> 00:36:45.037 line:80%
My life is like a well-written novel.

393
00:36:49.124 --> 00:36:52.419 line:80%
But if Kang Ji-won is
the one wrong sentence in it...

394
00:36:54.546 --> 00:36:55.797 line:80%
How would you feel?

395
00:36:58.133 --> 00:36:59.843 line:80%
Don't talk nonsense. Get up.

396
00:37:01.511 --> 00:37:04.348 line:80%
It's short and crooked.

397
00:37:05.724 --> 00:37:08.185 line:80%
The content and writing is a mess too.

398
00:37:09.102 --> 00:37:11.939 line:80%
So it keeps catching my eye
and bothering me.

399
00:37:13.857 --> 00:37:15.859 line:80%
It opens to her page when thrown.

400
00:37:18.528 --> 00:37:22.407 line:80%
There's nothing special
to find or remember in my life.

401
00:37:23.659 --> 00:37:25.869 line:80%
But only that part is so clear.

402
00:37:31.541 --> 00:37:32.709 line:80%
Nevertheless...

403
00:37:36.505 --> 00:37:38.882 line:80%
You're more qualified.

404
00:37:42.552 --> 00:37:44.972 line:80%
Because you'll be alive after ten years.

405
00:38:15.794 --> 00:38:17.004 line:80%
