460
00:42:56.533 --> 00:42:58.785 line:80%
I WANT TO DO IT

461
00:43:06.751 --> 00:43:07.752 line:80%
Wait.

462
00:43:07.836 --> 00:43:09.254 line:80%
What? Why?

463
00:43:10.213 --> 00:43:11.214 line:80%
What will you do?

464
00:43:12.007 --> 00:43:14.634 line:80%
