-Come on...

473
00:43:37.490 --> 00:43:38.325 line:80%
Just a second.

474
00:43:46.833 --> 00:43:48.209 line:80%
Excuse me.

475
00:43:50.170 --> 00:43:51.796 line:80%
I'm the one in charge.

476
00:43:51.880 --> 00:43:53.256 line:80%
What's wrong?

477
00:43:53.340 --> 00:43:55.967 line:80%
My husband's allergic to pine nuts!

478
00:43:56.051 --> 00:43:58.720 line:80%
But there wasn't any allergy sign!

479
00:43:58.803 --> 00:44:00.430 line:80%
-What?
-What do we do?

480
00:44:00.930 --> 00:44:01.890 line:80%
Honey.

481
00:44:01.973 --> 00:44:03.516 line:80%
I'll get the allergy sign.

482
00:44:03.600 --> 00:44:05.560 line:80%
ALLERGEN LABELING:
PINE NUTS

483
00:44:06.811 --> 00:44:08.730 line:80%
He should go to the hospital.

484
00:44:16.154 --> 00:44:20.158 line:80%
You must've been so scared,
and it's impossible to make up for it,

485
00:44:22.243 --> 00:44:23.453 line:80%
but we apologize!

486
00:44:24.996 --> 00:44:28.583 line:80%
How could a big company like U&K
make such a mistake?

487
00:44:28.666 --> 00:44:30.543 line:80%
I just don't understand.

488
00:44:30.627 --> 00:44:31.753 line:80%
We're very sorry.

489
00:44:33.463 --> 00:44:37.175 line:80%
Let it go. Nothing happened.

490
00:44:37.258 --> 00:44:40.887 line:80%
Things like this can happen
while you work.

491
00:44:41.513 --> 00:44:42.389 line:80%
Yes, sir.

492
00:44:42.472 --> 00:44:44.599 line:80%
Since it's just us, we'll let it go.

493
00:44:44.682 --> 00:44:46.351 line:80%
If my daughter were here...

494
00:44:46.434 --> 00:44:48.353 line:80%
We apologize one more time.

495
00:44:55.402 --> 00:44:56.820 line:80%
Toss the receipt.

496
00:45:06.663 --> 00:45:08.998 line:80%
The ambulance fees and hospital bills.

497
00:45:09.082 --> 00:45:10.834 line:80%
But compensation too?

498
00:45:12.544 --> 00:45:17.173 line:80%
If he had such a dangerous allergy,
shouldn't he have been more careful?

499
00:45:17.257 --> 00:45:18.842 line:80%
Everyone likes money.

500
00:45:18.925 --> 00:45:21.428 line:80%
If the company finds out about this,

501
00:45:21.511 --> 00:45:23.430 line:80%
it'll be bad for us.

502
00:45:24.806 --> 00:45:27.809 line:80%
Paying them off is the easiest.

503
00:45:29.352 --> 00:45:32.480 line:80%
Still, you spent
so much of your own money.

504
00:45:32.564 --> 00:45:35.733 line:80%
It's okay. It's me!

505
00:45:35.817 --> 00:45:38.069 line:80%
I've gotten a good return on stocks.

506
00:45:38.153 --> 00:45:39.612 line:80%
-The CEO of TKU,
-So... What?

507
00:45:39.696 --> 00:45:43.450 line:80%
Oh Chang-gyu, fled overseas,
and it's been revealed only now.

508
00:45:43.533 --> 00:45:45.702 line:80%
A political emergency is happening.

509
00:45:45.785 --> 00:45:49.330 line:80%
Oh was once investigated
for his relationship with politician Choi.

510
00:45:49.414 --> 00:45:52.292 line:80%
He claimed he was innocent,
expressing his...

511
00:45:52.375 --> 00:45:54.210 line:80%
According to TMB's coverage,

512
00:45:54.294 --> 00:45:57.088 line:80%
it's been 27 days
since he fled the country.

513
00:45:57.172 --> 00:45:59.799 line:80%
It has been revealed that TKU employees

514
00:45:59.883 --> 00:46:02.594 line:80%
haven't been paid wages for two months.

515
00:46:05.096 --> 00:46:07.724 line:80%
What do I do? Seriously? Damn it!

516
00:46:08.766 --> 00:46:11.019 line:80%
How about selling everything now?

517
00:46:11.102 --> 00:46:12.187 line:80%
Who will buy it?

518
00:46:15.482 --> 00:46:17.734 line:80%
I already put it up for sale.

519
00:46:17.817 --> 00:46:19.986 line:80%
But everyone's trying to sell now.

520
00:46:21.446 --> 00:46:23.156 line:80%
Then what do you have to do?

521
00:46:25.450 --> 00:46:27.035 line:80%
The transaction will be...

522
00:46:27.118 --> 00:46:29.162 line:80%
Why are you asking? So annoying!

523
00:46:30.622 --> 00:46:33.791 line:80%
Then you can't get a cent?

524
00:46:40.965 --> 00:46:41.799 line:80%
Ji-won.

525
00:46:43.134 --> 00:46:46.429 line:80%
The situation is much more serious
than you think.

526
00:46:47.013 --> 00:46:48.097 line:80%
I used credit.

527
00:46:50.266 --> 00:46:52.352 line:80%
Credit? What do you mean?

528
00:46:52.435 --> 00:46:54.354 line:80%
Then what do you have to do?

529
00:46:57.232 --> 00:47:00.360 line:80%
What's the point of talking to you?

530
00:47:05.448 --> 00:47:06.449 line:80%
Yes, Ms. Yang.

531
00:47:08.159 --> 00:47:10.578 line:80%
Yes, I'm in the bathroom.

532
00:47:12.664 --> 00:47:15.083 line:80%
You dummy. The credit isn't important.

533
00:47:16.793 --> 00:47:19.128 line:80%
I even took out a private loan.

534
00:47:19.921 --> 00:47:22.048 line:80%
He didn't mention the private loan.

535
00:47:22.131 --> 00:47:23.508 line:80%
He didn't before too.

536
00:47:23.591 --> 00:47:27.512 line:80%
He never says things to hurt his pride.
He's not the type.

537
00:47:29.514 --> 00:47:31.724 line:80%
Just in case, keep an eye on him.

538
00:47:34.852 --> 00:47:35.979 line:80%
I loved you.

539
00:47:40.024 --> 00:47:41.192 line:80%
What are you doing?

540
00:47:43.403 --> 00:47:45.071 line:80%
Was it our fate

541
00:47:45.738 --> 00:47:48.074 line:80%
to be a threesome, not just two of us?

542
00:47:49.701 --> 00:47:52.620 line:80%
Are you possessed? I don't understand you.

543
00:47:57.584 --> 00:48:00.128 line:80%
I'm going to marry Ji-won.

544
00:48:01.337 --> 00:48:02.922 line:80%
If we had more time,

545
00:48:03.506 --> 00:48:06.092 line:80%
I would've fallen for you completely.

546
00:48:06.175 --> 00:48:08.261 line:80%
But this fate puts the brake down.

547
00:48:10.221 --> 00:48:11.222 line:80%
Then...

548
00:48:13.433 --> 00:48:14.851 line:80%
Goodbye.

549
00:48:18.229 --> 00:48:19.939 line:80%
So keep my mouth shut?

550
00:48:22.525 --> 00:48:23.568 line:80%
What?

551
00:48:27.947 --> 00:48:29.073 line:80%
I won't...

552
00:48:33.161 --> 00:48:36.414 line:80%
say anything, Min-hwan. Don't worry.

553
00:48:37.957 --> 00:48:41.169 line:80%
I just want you to be happy.

554
00:48:43.296 --> 00:48:44.380 line:80%
What?

555
00:48:45.757 --> 00:48:46.633 line:80%
Happy?

556
00:49:02.899 --> 00:49:05.026 line:80%
Why does life suck so bad?

557
00:49:05.109 --> 00:49:06.319 line:80%
Drink slowly.

558
00:49:09.405 --> 00:49:10.323 line:80%
Hey.

559
00:49:12.992 --> 00:49:14.285 line:80%
Do you like me?

560
00:49:19.248 --> 00:49:20.625 line:80%
Of course, I do.

561
00:49:23.044 --> 00:49:26.756 line:80%
Thank you for liking someone like me.

562
00:49:32.970 --> 00:49:36.307 line:80%
You said to drink slowly, so I should.

563
00:49:38.726 --> 00:49:39.977 line:80%
I'm sorry.

564
00:49:41.646 --> 00:49:44.190 line:80%
I wanted to marry you next year,

565
00:49:45.775 --> 00:49:46.984 line:80%
but what's left...

566
00:49:48.444 --> 00:49:50.655 line:80%
is the Han River for me.

567
00:49:51.447 --> 00:49:54.283 line:80%
He's asking for money
in such a literary way.

568
00:50:00.248 --> 00:50:01.249 line:80%
Damn it!

569
00:50:01.874 --> 00:50:05.378 line:80%
You're young. You can earn it again.
I'm in no rush.

570
00:50:08.715 --> 00:50:10.800 line:80%
You can't say that.

571
00:50:10.883 --> 00:50:14.887 line:80%
Think of your age. What about kids?

572
00:50:14.971 --> 00:50:16.639 line:80%
You don't want any kids.

573
00:50:16.723 --> 00:50:19.016 line:80%
You're more important to me.

574
00:50:19.934 --> 00:50:21.352 line:80%
That's true.

575
00:50:22.437 --> 00:50:24.605 line:80%
I'm a third-generation only son.

576
00:50:24.689 --> 00:50:26.691 line:80%
How can I only think of myself?

577
00:50:26.774 --> 00:50:28.526 line:80%
That's true.

578
00:50:29.360 --> 00:50:31.362 line:80%
Then what should we do?

579
00:50:39.328 --> 00:50:40.246 line:80%
Ji-won?

580
00:50:42.790 --> 00:50:44.125 line:80%
Shall we get married?

581
00:50:47.378 --> 00:50:50.089 line:80%
I can't give you a glamorous life
as I planned.

582
00:50:51.466 --> 00:50:56.596 line:80%
But we'll be
a better family tomorrow than we are now.

583
00:50:57.722 --> 00:50:59.182 line:80%
I promise.

584
00:51:05.354 --> 00:51:06.355 line:80%
Family?

585
00:51:07.190 --> 00:51:08.149 line:80%
Family.

586
00:51:08.733 --> 00:51:12.695 line:80%
I know you get weak when I mention family.

587
00:51:12.779 --> 00:51:18.326 line:80%
What a crappy way to say you'll sponge off
me for life. You call that family?

588
00:51:20.578 --> 00:51:23.706 line:80%
It took courage for me to say that.
What's with you?

589
00:51:25.208 --> 00:51:27.418 line:80%
Is it because I'm broke now?

590
00:51:28.419 --> 00:51:30.630 line:80%
You're not that type of snob.

591
00:51:37.845 --> 00:51:38.971 line:80%
How funny, right?

592
00:51:39.847 --> 00:51:42.016 line:80%
He wants to marry without a penny.

593
00:51:42.517 --> 00:51:46.437 line:80%
No, he must want to marry me
now that he's broke.

594
00:51:48.731 --> 00:51:50.525 line:80%
This is the same as before.

595
00:51:51.526 --> 00:51:55.321 line:80%
He proposed to me, saying
he'd invest with his parents' money.

596
00:51:59.450 --> 00:52:03.120 line:80%
My debt started to get bigger
when that went south.

597
00:52:03.204 --> 00:52:07.333 line:80%
But he was the person I chose,
so I thought we'd work it out together.

598
00:52:08.084 --> 00:52:10.211 line:80%
He was selfish.

599
00:52:11.963 --> 00:52:15.007 line:80%
Anyway, all my choices were backwards.

600
00:52:31.691 --> 00:52:33.609 line:80%
You'll get fat if you eat like that.

601
00:52:40.241 --> 00:52:45.538 line:80%
I used to give a stray cat food
in college.

602
00:52:48.249 --> 00:52:50.209 line:80%
I wanted to bring him home,

603
00:52:51.085 --> 00:52:54.005 line:80%
but I was scared
I couldn't raise him properly.

604
00:52:54.922 --> 00:52:55.923 line:80%
Then...

605
00:52:57.466 --> 00:53:00.344 line:80%
the cat disappeared one day.

606
00:53:00.428 --> 00:53:01.971 line:80%
It was a cold winter.

607
00:53:02.763 --> 00:53:05.391 line:80%
I regretted it so much then.

608
00:53:08.769 --> 00:53:11.731 line:80%
He was so tiny. Like this big.

609
00:53:12.607 --> 00:53:14.483 line:80%
He had such a temper.

610
00:53:16.652 --> 00:53:19.780 line:80%
He got chased away
after trying to fight other cats.

611
00:53:21.157 --> 00:53:24.201 line:80%
He hated people,
so I don't think anyone took him.

612
00:53:37.089 --> 00:53:38.549 line:80%
To tell the truth,

613
00:53:39.258 --> 00:53:41.010 line:80%
I was discharged early.

614
00:53:42.136 --> 00:53:44.472 line:80%
It was similar to a car accident.

615
00:53:46.349 --> 00:53:48.476 line:80%
Similar to a car accident?

616
00:54:10.873 --> 00:54:12.792 line:80%
Are you okay?

617
00:54:12.875 --> 00:54:13.918 line:80%
Yeah, I'm fine.

618
00:54:23.135 --> 00:54:24.136 line:80%
Are you okay?

619
00:54:33.354 --> 00:54:34.855 line:80%
I ruptured my knee ligaments.

620
00:54:39.819 --> 00:54:42.863 line:80%
I jumped in front of a car to save a cat.

621
00:54:42.947 --> 00:54:44.532 line:80%
I didn't get hit, though.

622
00:54:50.121 --> 00:54:51.288 line:80%
Then...

623
00:54:53.708 --> 00:54:56.794 line:80%
the cat you're raising now...

624
00:54:57.795 --> 00:54:59.797 line:80%
It was the winter of 2005.

625
00:55:01.882 --> 00:55:04.635 line:80%
A cheese tabby with a bad temper.

626
00:55:07.763 --> 00:55:09.098 line:80%
Doesn't like people.

627
00:55:23.696 --> 00:55:25.573 line:80%
Are you going to work out?

628
00:55:26.615 --> 00:55:27.783 line:80%
Hello?

629
00:55:28.325 --> 00:55:29.410 line:80%
Where'd they go?

630
00:55:30.703 --> 00:55:33.873 line:80%
Was it you? It was you all along!

631
00:55:34.957 --> 00:55:37.960 line:80%
I thought you looked similar.
It was really you!

632
00:55:39.587 --> 00:55:41.172 line:80%
It's 20130419.

633
00:55:41.756 --> 00:55:42.798 line:80%
My passcode.

634
00:55:42.882 --> 00:55:44.091 line:80%
Come anytime.

635
00:55:44.842 --> 00:55:46.177 line:80%
Really? Can I?

636
00:55:47.470 --> 00:55:49.889 line:80%
Let's see each other more often!

637
00:55:51.849 --> 00:55:52.975 line:80%
You're so cute!

638
00:56:01.776 --> 00:56:04.612 line:80%
Either way, Mr. Park must get married now.

639
00:56:06.197 --> 00:56:09.033 line:80%
Yes. Since he needs
to get money from his family.

640
00:56:11.327 --> 00:56:15.873 line:80%
His debts are probably
about half a billion won in total.

641
00:56:15.956 --> 00:56:18.084 line:80%
Maybe more.

642
00:56:19.418 --> 00:56:21.337 line:80%
It was worthwhile lending him

643
00:56:21.420 --> 00:56:24.381 line:80%
my money to make him go all in with TKU.

644
00:56:24.924 --> 00:56:28.969 line:80%
But at this rate, I don't think
he'll give up marrying you.

645
00:56:31.263 --> 00:56:33.224 line:80%
So I came up with this plan.

646
00:56:35.434 --> 00:56:36.477 line:80%
Although,

647
00:56:38.562 --> 00:56:40.773 line:80%
I'll have to get his crappy proposal.

648
00:56:44.318 --> 00:56:46.779 line:80%
It must be so annoying for me, right?

649
00:56:46.862 --> 00:56:50.407 line:80%
But if I want to live a long life,
I must work hard.

650
00:56:53.285 --> 00:56:55.204 line:80%
He proposed on my birthday.

651
00:56:55.913 --> 00:57:00.084 line:80%
Everything he did was tolerable back then.

652
00:57:00.751 --> 00:57:01.752 line:80%
But I hated it.

653
00:57:02.670 --> 00:57:04.296 line:80%
One, two, three.

654
00:57:40.916 --> 00:57:42.710 line:80%
I have to see that again?

655
00:57:45.337 --> 00:57:46.422 line:80%
Terrible, right?

656
00:57:46.505 --> 00:57:50.342 line:80%
It's my first birthday after being reborn.

657
00:57:59.810 --> 00:58:01.353 line:80%
Ji-hyuk did?

658
00:58:01.437 --> 00:58:03.022 line:80%
Yes, sir.

659
00:58:03.105 --> 00:58:04.607 line:80%
Oh, right. Also...

660
00:58:12.323 --> 00:58:13.365 line:80%
NECESSITY OF R&D

661
00:58:13.449 --> 00:58:15.451 line:80%
TEST FLIGHT RESULTS

662
00:58:15.534 --> 00:58:18.120 line:80%
Wait, so this technology is possible?

663
00:58:18.204 --> 00:58:21.999 line:80%
Apparently, the development team says
we can finally try it.

664
00:58:22.875 --> 00:58:26.128 line:80%
As you can see,
those are the test flight results.

665
00:58:28.088 --> 00:58:30.299 line:80%
U&K Aerobotics.

666
00:58:30.382 --> 00:58:32.051 line:80%
Shall I secure more stocks?

667
00:58:32.134 --> 00:58:34.261 line:80%
If this is possible, of course.

668
00:58:34.345 --> 00:58:36.347 line:80%
That's that. About Ji-hyuk again.

669
00:58:39.516 --> 00:58:42.561 line:80%
What on earth is he thinking right now?

670
00:59:23.185 --> 00:59:24.186 line:80%
Ji-won?

671
00:59:30.109 --> 00:59:31.777 line:80%
Min-hwan, what is all--

672
00:59:35.281 --> 00:59:36.532 line:80%
Don't say anything.

673
00:59:38.158 --> 00:59:40.035 line:80%
Tonight's for you.

674
00:59:44.290 --> 00:59:45.416 line:80%
My princess.

675
00:59:53.257 --> 00:59:54.258 line:80%
Kang Ji-won.

676
01:00:02.725 --> 01:00:03.934 line:80%
I love you.

677
01:00:36.216 --> 01:00:37.343 line:80%
Let me.

678
01:00:50.272 --> 01:00:54.109 line:80%
I'll do everything I can for you, Ji-won.

679
01:00:54.193 --> 01:00:56.570 line:80%
She won't know this is cubic, right?

680
01:00:56.653 --> 01:00:58.864 line:80%
But it's not like she'll toss it.

681
01:00:59.490 --> 01:01:02.951 line:80%
I won't let them marry.

682
01:01:04.203 --> 01:01:06.997 line:80%
You'd hate to see me happy.

683
01:01:16.632 --> 01:01:17.800 line:80%
Yes.

684
01:01:18.467 --> 01:01:21.220 line:80%
Please use whatever means necessary

685
01:01:23.430 --> 01:01:25.682 line:80%
to marry my husband.

686
01:01:40.948 --> 01:01:44.118 line:80%
Ji-won jumped in the water for me.

687
01:01:44.201 --> 01:01:45.285 line:80%
Ji-won.

688
01:01:46.078 --> 01:01:48.747 line:80%
It's your turn to make me happy.

689
01:01:50.582 --> 01:01:52.793 line:80%
It was the best first birthday.

690
01:01:54.795 --> 01:01:56.755 line:80%
I'm engaged!

691
01:01:57.339 --> 01:02:01.260 line:80%
I'm going to milk him
for the first and last time.

692
01:02:01.343 --> 01:02:02.803 line:80%
She bought all this?

693
01:02:02.886 --> 01:02:05.139 line:80%
My mother-in-law has high standards.

694
01:02:05.931 --> 01:02:07.015 line:80%
Why are you here?

695
01:02:07.099 --> 01:02:08.559 line:80%
Isn't the family meeting today?

696
01:02:09.560 --> 01:02:10.894 line:80%
I'm happy with now.

697
01:02:11.437 --> 01:02:16.316 line:80%
It's obvious what kind of family
she'll marry into.

698
01:02:22.906 --> 01:02:24.825 line:80%
Translated by Suyun Mounce

